snippet.title: Diana Pretend Cooking with New Kitchen Toy
snippet.description:
Diana is pretend cooking with a Minnie Mouse kitchen toyset! She is trying to fix her broken kitchen toy, but she can’t fix it. Diana buys new giant kitchen toy. Diana cooks pretend food for Dolls. She makes them cupcakes! Roma also wants to eat. He helps Diana to clear and cook with New Kitchen Toy.
